{"type": "article", "id": 23865, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-15T07:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 24893, "name": "Knog"}, {"id": 24894, "name": "HCWD Studio"}, {"id": 24895, "name": "Bios Urn"}, {"id": 24896, "name": "Ineke Hans"}, {"id": 24897, "name": "Tony Buckland"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607165701Jv7u9UC3l8Ehc4DK.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>plof by Ineke Hans</h2>\n<p>这把带脚蹬的沙发是由丹麦设计师 Ineke Hans 为比利时设计品牌 Moome 设计的。它的外形非常方正，厚实的软垫让沙发看上去像一个沙袋。金属结构和沙发本身都是统一的黄色，连成一个整体，让沙袋的气体看起来更大，也使人感受到轻松。当初设计时，设计师只想做一个放垫子的结构，而名字 “plof” 的意思是重重地落下。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145623NmLPhEC0VYK3Iyek.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145624M4mQ5lPFjoHvWciC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88675214\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061456240B9iobCNDhvwsqQP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66773504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145625eN9HYAkXrJ0ltcgi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145625UAx52GbtyKPSeHNn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66773504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Oi by Knog </h2>\n<p>澳大利亚品牌 Knog 专门做自行车配件，这个像戒指一样的圆环是自行车铃铛。它的特点就是小巧，只有 15 毫米宽，通过螺丝安装，改变了原本车铃笨重的感觉，车铃几乎是隐藏的。在声音上，它能产生几个音调。有铝、黄铜、青铜、钛等 5 种材料和大小两种直径。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/-oi/oi-the-bike-bell-that-doesnt-look-like-a-bike-bell?ref=project_link\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145625vcZ8kPy3VgNKQsWl.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56259205\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145628VLpgUtlZvDPyGAhB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50441176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145628Ez1FdgoIOZ7U05Lu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61891117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145629dNpRSDM6asiT054Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145629v0ObLqAFkz78QxTj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145629LGI6d4efycmUKQ3b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<h2>SPLIT &amp; Bent Bench by HCWD Studio</h2>\n<p>这盏灯有行星绕着轨道旋转的感觉，一个双面圆镜将手工吹制而成的玻璃球面倾斜切开，也将光线一分为二，但因为镜面反射，光线仍然是发散出来的，并没有被遮挡。而倾斜切割的镜面给人一种摇摆和失重的瞬间。除此之外，他们设计了一个有些微微弯曲的凳子，似乎有很多人已经坐过了，给人一种亲近感。HCWD Studio（ 炘工作室）在纽约，由两位华裔设计师组成，<a href=\"http://www.hcwangdesign.com/blog/\">这里是工作室链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145630U0alV6DAoWzrb2N5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061456303pwfqXuyYG6l8xzC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145631YkQyixqzargcf37e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64270833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145631Vgj1aICbnM7OURdX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145631D4yUCwYWb9fVsaFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.603125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Bios Incube by Bios Urn</h2>\n<p>这个白色的花瓶是一个孵化器，设计师的想法是将骨灰放在其中，通过自然降解滋养植物。花瓶有两层，中间含有储水系统，可以通过特殊装置自动浇水。他们认为对逝者缅怀的最好方式是看到回归自然和新生，这也是一种经济环保的方式。西班牙的设计师早在 1997 年就提出了，直到 2013 年才生产出产品，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/biosurn/bios-incube-the-worlds-first-incubator-for-the-aft\">它目前正在众筹。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145632cq2RlmGHuC3NWV5T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145632Pa0Dy6f4TwLYKkGd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145633tpw4LaNkufoq8DMz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145633HkfVraNgq9d45SLb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145633w3jSP0kDzMvGVIui.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>CityShuttle by 未行</h2>\n<p>这款背包来自一个叫“未行”的团队，他们从渔夫的下水服的材料中获得灵感设计。背包的形状近似一个旅行箱，很方正，可以完全摊开使用。渔衣面料有着舒适的触感，除了防水耐磨外还有明亮的色泽。这款包命名为“都市穿梭” (CityShuttle)，可以适合旅行办公等多个功能。产品目前还没有上市。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145634YaXn3G42fMUkxr96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145634jLoqkyezvI6mBNrU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145635MnYJcF9US5qvxiTV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145635s48dR2K9lx7Ntqmr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145636tAne1X8sR9xH6C0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“birds of minnesota”by Tony Buckland</h2>\n<p>这是一组关于鸟类的插图设计，美国明尼阿波利斯的设计师 Tony Buckland 根据明尼苏达州的 24 种常见鸟类设计，每种鸟都可看做不同的几何图形组成，鸟的身体是梯形的，鼻子是三角形，通过不同的颜色突出其个性特征，又保持了一种整体的极简美感。这些图案都可以出售，售价 20 美元起，这里是<a href=\"http://www.birdsofminnesota.com\">网站主页</a>和<a href=\"https://society6.com/tonybuckland\">购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145636SbxakuVG3qtzKOsI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145636sIg2EjDvSfpwYP3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061456375fTA0gZaMo3yFkEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145637jVZKX9HEw8xqlfPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061456376bqcx9UnlpoueFs4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}